contact_address: Level 5, Medical Research Foundation (MRF) Building, 50 Murray Street
contact_department: Centre for Genetic Origins of Health and Disease
contact_laboratory: Centre for Genetic Origins of Health and Disease
data_processing: Background noise subtracted using GenomeStudio (v2010.2), Gene Expression Module (v1.7.0), Data then log2-transformed and quantile normalised with lumi R package (Bioconductor) on R.
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted from decidual samples using Rneasy Midi kits (Qiagen) following manufacturer's protocol. hyb_protocol: Illumina's Whole-Genome Gene Expression Direct Hybridisation assay protocol
label_protocol_ch1: Illumina's Whole-Genome Gene Expression Direct Hybridisation assay protocol (includes labelling method)
scan_protocol: Scanned using Illumina iScan System with iScan Control Software (v3.2.45)
treatment_protocol_ch1: Harvested decidual tissue was placed in RNA-later for at least 24 hours at 4C. Decidual tissue was then removed from RNA-later and stored at -80OC.
